      "id": 12,
      "options": {
        "content": "### PFE anomaly demo usage\\n\\nUse this dashboard during attack/failure simulation. Examples:\\n\\n- Stop Web service/container → failed HTTP/TCP probes increase.\\n- Stop DNS service/container → DNS TCP/query probes fail.\\n- Disconnect or stop an SNMP device → SNMP devices down increases.\\n- Break an active interface → admin-up interface down indicator increases.\\n- Generate traffic/errors → latency or interface error panels change.\\n\\nThe Python analyzer/Jenkins remediation can later consume the same Prometheus signals shown here.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
